# The LOD fixture + query + shapes are byte-compared by lod_acceptance.py (B1
# lossless-round-trip). Pin LF so a fresh checkout matches the LF the generator
# emits on every platform -- an autocrlf CRLF checkout would fail B1 spuriously.
*.ttl        text eol=lf
*.rq         text eol=lf
fixture.keys text eol=lf
